      "plot_summary": "The Doctor, Tegan, and Turlough land on Frontios, a human colony plagued by mysterious deaths and meteorite bombardments. They discover the TARDIS has been destroyed and face the alien Tractators, who plan to use the colony as part of their domination strategy. The group must work with the colonists to uncover the truth while battling the alien menace."
